Subject: Virtual Appliance EoL?
Description:
Hi Support,

We have been done a review of the applications and appliances in use in our network and we noticed that our Endpoint Protect VM is running Ubuntu 18.04.6 LTS which seems to be end of life? Is there a newer version of the VM we need to migrate to?

Kind Regards,
Andrew
Solution_Comment__c: The customer migrated to a new Epp server VM running ubuntu 22.04.
